summary: Unrelenting shout replacer for females, uses my gf\'s voice
descriptionHtml:
Replaces Fus Roh Dah with Fah Que Doosh. Just a fun little replacement mod that I made when my gf told me about a dream she had where she was using fah que! as a shout. She provided the voice for the shout as well. Check the video section for the preview!

THIS MODS ONLY THE FEMALE FUS RO DAH SHOUT

To install, just extract the sound folder to skyrim/data.
To Uninstall delete it.

Use Nexus Mod Manager its great!

Special thanks goes to Lurtzello the maker of \"This is Sparta\" and \"Firin Mah Lazer\" shout replacements. Without those mods to look at I never would have figured out the proper way to name and splice the sound files. 

I used xWMAEncode for making the xwm files as well as fuz_extractor to make the fuz files. 

This Is Sparta by Lurtzello - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1294
Voice file extractor by Agnahim - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=950
author: Kelticfury
